        Selling in Chermside West 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Chermside West's elevated streets, the Marchant Park sports and recreation precinct, and the quieter family character set it apart from its busier retail-anchor neighbour. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Body -->
